lead_paragraph: Panathinaikos, Red Star Belgrade and Laboral Kutxa Vitoria advanced to the Euroleague playoffs with a match to spare, while holders Real Madrid were staring at an early exit after some exciting action on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Trio Book Euroleague Playoff Berths as Real Falter
